title: Concerns for Titans; Craziest Draft Moments; NFL Prospect, Coby Bryant
itunes:title: Concerns for Titans; Craziest Draft Moments; NFL Prospect, Coby Bryant
description:
The latest edition of The Good Morning Football Podcast explores how concerned the Tennessee Titans should be about Ryan Tannehill and A.J. Brown. Hosts Kay Adams, Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt, and former Super Bowl champion, Shaun O'Hara react to Ryan Tannehill missing voluntary workouts. Then they share which teams in the NFL Draft can't miss on their draft pick; they dive into the most shocking draft moments in NFL history, and they finish up being joined by NFL prospect, Coby Bryant, and he shares how Kobe has influenced him and he reacts to Jalen Ramsey's tweet about him.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
